      • getHeightMaps

        com.flowpowered.nbt.CompoundTag getHeightMaps()
        Returns the height maps of the chunk. If it's a pre 1.13 world, a IntArrayTag containing the height map will be stored inside here by the name of 'heightMap'.
        Returns:
        A CompoundTag containing all the height maps of the chunk.

      • getBiomes

        int[] getBiomes()
        Returns all the biomes of the chunk. In case it's a pre 1.13 world, every int inside the array will contain two biomes, and should be converted into a byte[].
        Returns:
        A int[] containing all the biomes of the chunk.
